headline: Fifth Third hires ex-M&T CFO to lead regional banking
summary: Darren King will “drive strategy, cultivate talent and pursue growth” as Fifth Third pushes southeast, the bank said. He succeeds Kris Garrett, the lender’s retiring wealth and asset manager.
